{"tid":1103110,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［LIVE］捷克六日遊","createTime":"2019-04-12T07:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T15:49:55.000Z","uid":242723,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9a78a8b41ce67a668567dc0f97a684f33733f070","tid":1103110,"uid":242723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:43:26.000Z","msg":"其實上年已經去過成個星期捷克 睇返原來成個trip去咗四個UNESCO 搵下搵下資料發現成個捷克一共有12個UNESCO 就挑起咗我挑戰欲 想成功打卡哂12個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以今次會K.O.多三個UNESCO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由Prague到Brno留幾日 再上Olomouc 係Ostrava畫上句點<br />\n<br />\n本身無打算再去布拉格 上次已經去過四日 無話特別鐘意 成個城市都係韓國人大陸人台灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係朋友未去過捷克 所以就陪佢留一日布拉格布拉格<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRDQxPN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRDQxPN.png&h=93b8d80c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KV1uOn9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKV1uOn9.png&h=eea652e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zZHaxPR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzZHaxPR.png&h=04547c18&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gorR1Jd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgorR1Jd.png&h=983f2314&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b44bdc2be1766ebb78aa28a9a88f936804ba05a4","tid":1103110,"uid":242723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:54:49.000Z","msg":"琴日先上哂堂考完試 打算趕下assignment先再執喼 可能前日通頂 結果做下做下有啲眼瞓 就打算瞓兩個鐘再起身執喼<br />\n<br />\n兩個鐘後係醒咗 但係又想閉目養神多十五分鐘<br />\n<br />\n再醒已經係朋友係lobby等緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n距離班火車仲有九個字 於是瘋狂塞嘢入個喼 而家諗返都好多嘢執漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果要搭uber到火車站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以平時我寧願坐耐啲搭火車 都唔鐘意搭飛機係有理由的<br />\n火車早五分鐘到車站都仲得<br />\n去機場預多兩個鐘 到咗又要出市區 計返都仲耐過搭火車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b028ad7cd9473998e165720680bf829ac6adb613","tid":1103110,"uid":242723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:14:40.000Z","msg":"去程係搭regiojet火車<br />\n<br />\n個人而言真係呢間捷克公司嘅擁躉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先只要係ISIC student去捷克或者捷克境內線都有25折<br />\n係 真係25折<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多時候由城市去小鎮 一程都唔使一歐 揀位又唔使加錢 認真扺玩<br />\n<br />\n佢大部分巴士都有同飛機一樣有觸屏 有戲睇有game玩 仲有免費茶水咖啡 講緊係短至一個鐘嘅車程 真係好過flixbus多多聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過火車就比較殘舊 不過都過得去 買low cost定時定候有人派水<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URXFaNL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURXFaNL.png&h=b090042b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個廁所係一踩腳踏 啲排泄物直落路軌 回歸自然個種舊火車 而且個廁所中間有個窿睇到路軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TFb6QJN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTFb6QJN.png&h=2e2771ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隻窗都幾污糟"},{"pid":"4ada07cf53e9b8dbb3a2091ace0a0ef95b514026","tid":1103110,"uid":123922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"留名6月去Prague"},{"pid":"3ee6f6b97d10cd986433da7cca4fe1d8deb3f6b1","tid":1103110,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:49:55.000Z","msg":"CK 布拉格 kelvo 呢d公廁地點就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}